pybind11 submodule has been installed
git submodule add https://github.com/pybind/pybind11.git extern/pybind11

When initializing the repo view, please run the update:
git submodule update --init --recursive

To build the C++ modules:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make

To run, for example, prob/game.py, cd to prob and run "PYTHONPATH=..:../build python game.py"
